<h2> Notes </h2>

<p>
When a verb denotes a momentary action or movement, the time when it occurs is marked by <strong>@HI{{ni}}</strong>.
<strong>@HI{{ni}}</strong> is used when the noun before it uses a numeral; if the noun does not use a numeral then
the particle is not used. <strong>@HI{{ni}}</strong> may optionally be used with days of the week.
</p>

